<paragraph id="F7DA1FBF2F36BD9B7E57A8CE9D369E94" pageId="0" pageNumber="139">Due to of the few males available (only three, excluding the holotype), we were unable to obtain even a partial evertion of the endophallus (read below for more comments).</paragraph>
